Package: underwriter
Title: Automated Underwriting from Insurance Claim History
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Seokhoon", family = "Joo", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "seokhoonj@gmail.com")
Description: A data.table pipeline that cleanses insurance claim history,
    maps diagnosis codes to representative diseases, aggregates per-insured
    underwriting inputs, matches them against a rule set, and combines the
    per-disease decisions into a final per-insured underwriting decision.
    The engine is data-agnostic: rule sets and decision-code tables are supplied
    at run time, so it is not tied to any one insurer.
